init_text: Your entire life, you've been told you're deathly allergic to bees. You've always had people protecting you from them, be it your mother or a hired hand. Today, one slips through and lands on your shoulder. You hear a tiny voice say "Your Majesty, what are your orders?"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The bee continues "Madam, I am here to guard you and carry out your orders.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The bee responds "All bees can talk, your majesty.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The bee responds "We can do anything you need.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "It will be done" and lifts off the ground, and flies into your cupboard.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He replies matter of factly "You are not allergic to bees.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: you are the Queen of Bees."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He says "You are the queen of all the bees in this area.
